Admin Order Notifier: Single or multiple emails in a following form "Firstname Lastname <email>", like "Branko Ajzele <branko@inchoo.net>", without quotation marks. In case of multiple entries, each entry goes on separate line.
订单通知邮件: 单个或多个“姓名<邮件地址>”格式的邮件地址，如“Branko Ajzele <ajzele@gmail.net>”，不包括引号。在多个邮件地址的情况下，一个邮件地址占一行。
